Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + Wait' across all cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C2305210> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + Wait' leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration difference between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Closed' compared to 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' for cases with 'High' impact
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait' leading to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Maximum duration of 'Accepted + Wait' before transitioning to any 'Completed' status
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait' during weekdays vs weekends
Earliest occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait' in a case timeline
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Latest occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait' in a case timeline before case closure
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x00000221C2305210> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Average elapsed time between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
